39
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:19,010
Don't flatter yourself.

40
00:03:19,190 --> 00:03:20,870
You haven't paid me back for the ice cream.

41
00:03:20,910 --> 00:03:21,750
What a man.

42
00:03:22,070 --> 00:03:24,140
Don't charge to my card when you go to the cyber cafe next time.

43
00:03:24,910 --> 00:03:25,870
No problem.

44
00:03:25,900 --> 00:03:27,660
The next time you ask me to wash your swimming trunks after you are done,

45
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:28,840
I'll charge you 10 yuan each time.

46
00:03:29,070 --> 00:03:29,900
That's great.

47
00:03:29,930 --> 00:03:32,010
From now on, my noodles are 50 yuan.

48
00:03:32,270 --> 00:03:33,250
Suit yourselves.

49
00:03:33,670 --> 00:03:35,110
