00:07:41,740 --> 00:07:44,000
And for all of you at No. 1 High School,

157
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:46,520
it's a miracle if you fail to do so.

158
00:07:48,120 --> 00:07:49,480
So students,

159
00:07:50,540 --> 00:07:52,630
in grade 12, as your senior year,

160
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:54,290
I hope you can

161
00:07:54,540 --> 00:07:55,670
work hard this year.

162
00:07:55,900 --> 00:07:57,310
At this time next year,

163
00:07:57,470 --> 00:08:00,140
I hope everyone gets your respective admission letters,

164
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:01,860
and meet each other at your universities.

165
00:08:02,270 --> 00:08:03,880
Are you confident?

166
00:08:04,030 --> 00:08:05,120
Yes.

167
00:08:05,270 --> 00:08:06,500
Are you confident?

168
00:08:06,550 --> 00:08:08,130
Yes!

169
00:08:06,640 --> 00:08:07,760
[Final battle in June, let's meet at Tsinghua and Peking]

170
00:08:09,540 --> 00:08:11,380
When there is a will, there is a way!

171
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:12,610
From now on,

172
00:08:11,540 --> 00:08:14,990
[Giving our best to prepare for the college entrance exam]

173
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:14,280
students in grade 12

174
00:08:14,340 --> 00:08:16,030
