198
00:09:14,590 --> 00:09:16,520
You've been trained well through these years.

199
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:17,790
Thank you.

200
00:09:19,380 --> 00:09:22,940
[Striving unceasingly with unwavering resolve]

201
