239
00:10:30,950 --> 00:10:31,830
Really?

240
00:10:31,830 --> 00:10:32,960
Of course.

241
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:33,840
You must keep your promise.

242
00:10:34,070 --> 00:10:34,870
Yes, I'll.

243
00:10:40,520 --> 00:10:41,800
