00:11:17,710 --> 00:11:19,150
our way of thinking,

264
00:11:20,650 --> 00:11:21,860
creativity,

265
00:11:22,070 --> 00:11:23,080
foresight,

266
00:11:23,350 --> 00:11:24,510
and future plans.

